
1. nacos配置
sbc-service-elastic.properties增加如下配置
   wm.elasticsearch.analyzer=wm_standard
   
sbc-service-empower.properties增加如下配置
    vop.pool.core=60
    vop.pool.max=500
    vop.pool.queue=60
    vop.pool.keepAlive=60
    vop.pool.name=vop-task-
   
2、esGoodsInfo.json 、esGoods.json 、esPointsGoodsInfo.json

   "analyzer": "ik_max_word" 替换成  "analyzer": "wm_standard"
   并且增加   "norms": false
   
   增加了商品副标题字段
    "goodsSubtitle": {
        "analyzer": "wm_standard",
        "norms": false,
        "type": "text"
    },

    

3、服务器安装新的分词器  elasticsearch-analysis-ansj-6.4.3.0-bugfix-ALPHA
   联系运维进行安装

4、更新完成需要操作删除原有es结构 然后重新初始化数据
    curl -XDELETE localhost:9200/es_goods
    curl -XDELETE localhost:9200/es_goods_info
    curl -XDELETE localhost:9200/es_points_goods_info

    o2o环境还需要执行如下

    curl -XDELETE localhost:9200/es_o2o_goods_info
    curl -XDELETE localhost:9200/es_o2o_goods

